sets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情景三<br />\n偽中立撚話唔想理政治, 只想生活<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:&quot;總之我乜都唔想理! 俾返之前既生活我!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:&quot;屌! 咪係囉! 最衰都係政府! 咩五大壽頭應承咪好囉! 我想平平靜靜呀!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪好簡單! 我地只係講事實!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}